OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy morning of
OL,6,Fshowers for Orkney, with fresh
OL,7,Fwesterly winds. Otherwise a mainly dry
OL,8,Fday with good sunny spells extending
OL,9,Ffrom Shetland to Orkney for the
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMainly dry with occasional
OL,13,Flate sunshine. Cloud increasing
OL,14,Fovernight to bring some scattered
OL,15,Flight showers before dawn. Northerly
OL,16,Fwinds increasing fresh to strong.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSunday:FNortherly winds bringing
OL,19,Fmainly cloudy skies and a few light
OL,20,Fshowers, though most of these will be
OL,21,Fconfined to Shetland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
