OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,6,Fmainly dry with some limited brighter
OL,7,Fspells and light winds. Tuesday and
OL,8,FWednesday cloudy with occasional areas
OL,9,Fof rain crossing from the south.
